  {Title}Description{/Title}
{para}
This function is analagous to {Phrase Role="var"}append-path{/Phrase}, but works
on a directory as it's right-hand-side argument.  That is,
the function computes the directory referred to when {Parameter}dir2{/Parameter}
is interpreted relative to {Parameter}dir1{/Parameter}.{/para}
{para}
If {Parameter}dir2{/Parameter} is an absolute path, then it is returned.  Otherwise,
a new directory-name object is constructed.{/para}
